    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2018-05-23</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2019-09-10T16:27:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Budget, No Vacation Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits Congress from recessing, adjourning, considering other matters, or spending funds on official travel beginning on August 1 of each year until both chambers have passed a congressional budget resolution and all of the regular appropriations bills for the next fiscal year. The bill also sets forth requirements for regular quorum calls in the Senate until the budget and appropriations process has been completed. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>No Budget, No Vacation Act</title>
    <titles>
